                                (Things repeat rules must be re-created by hand)
- atlas-expanded instances of recurring routines (same title, same project,
  non-recurring due) are SKIPPED as machine-generated duplicates
- Section / time-of-day / duration -> appended note lines

Idempotent: progress in migration-log.jsonl; reruns skip completed ops.
